column15: American Tourister - Laptop Backpack CITI PRO PR 6L - GREY: Amazon.in: Computers & Accessories
column17:
Product Description

Innovative Compartments Beside the padded compartment that can hold up to 15.4" laptop the American Tourister Citi-Pro is designed with smart sleeves and organizer panels that allows you to keep your documents stationaries and mobile devices at the same time. Keep all your items organized in the same backpack without having to use separate bag storing them. Lightweight & Durable Made from polyester material the American Tourister Citi-Pro is designed for both men and women and providing durability ideal for you that are always on-the-go. The smart briefcase also comes with padded shoulder strap that ensures comfort during prolonged carrying. Extra Features The American Tourister Citi-Pro allows you to listen to music on the go with the earphone access and keeping your bag dry with the rain cover that prevents water from seeping into it while it is raining. The air comfort plus technology of the backpack ensure your backpack dry and clean. About American Tourister Started in 1933 the founder Sol Koffler aimed to produce a tough suitcase that could sell for a dollar. American Tourister introduces Hi-Taper luggage during the initial year of air travel era and continue with innovative luggage design and material. The world's first molded luggage is then produced and undergo "flight test" and the hardside product is also put to test by the toughest critic a gorilla. In 1993 American Tourister was acquired by Samsonite marking the union of two of the world's great luggage brands
